 *     - $120 commercial-diagnostic note removed from pricing footer
 *     - FAQ Q7 (commercial appliances) removed (6 questions remain)
 *     - Sub-Zero pricing card kept as residential luxury (NOT commercial)
 *     - 4-card pricing set: diagnostic / standard / luxury / warranty
 *
 * NAP & Rating Policy SSOT compliance:
 *   - aggregateRating omitted from schema
 *   - streetAddress omitted (RC is service_area, not physical_pin)
 *
 * Cat B `note` field on jobs: appended to job body verbatim.
 */

